      "text": [
        "1497 - وَقَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «اَلرَّعْدُ صَوْتُ اَلْمَلَكِ وَ اَلْبَرْقُ سَوْطُهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1497 - Imam (as) said:\n\"The thunder is the voice of the angel, and the lightning is his whip.\""
        ]
      }
